    <item>
      <title>犯罪浪潮来袭 丹麦将加强瑞典边境管控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/denmark-to-tighten-swedish-border-control-after-crime-wave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦司法部长彼得·胡梅尔加德 (Peter Hummelgaard) 在 TV2 播出的采访中表示，随着哥本哈根发生的瑞典人枪击事件不断增加，丹麦将加强与瑞典边境的管控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/denmark-to-tighten-swedish-border-control-after-crime-wave</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 13:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
