      <title>卢拉官员称巴西必须削减预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/brazil-politics-budget-cuts-are-necessary-lula-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统府办公厅主任鲁伊·科斯塔周四在总统与内阁会议后告诉记者，鉴于总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦致力于履行财政责任，巴西有必要削减预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/brazil-politics-budget-cuts-are-necessary-lula-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 13:13:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
